        <h2>What is AeroSeal?</h2>
        <p>AeroSeal is a revolutionary duct sealing technology that seals leaks from the inside of your ductwork. Think of it like this: imagine your ductwork is like a garden hose with holes in it. Traditional methods try to find and patch each hole from the outside. AeroSeal works from the inside, automatically finding and sealing every leak, no matter how small or hard to reach.</p>

