        <h3>How It Works — The Science</h3>
        <p>AeroSeal uses a patented process that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Temporarily blocks your vents and registers</li>
          <li>Pressurizes your duct system with safe, non-toxic particles</li>
          <li>Forces particles to stick only at leak sites (not on duct walls)</li>
          <li>Builds up layers until leaks are completely sealed</li>
          <li>Provides real-time computer monitoring of the sealing process</li>
        </ul>

